ce without human availability 24/7. The chatbot is customizable to match brand aesthetics and provides insights into customer preferences for product and support enhancement. With different pricing plans, including a free option, Bottomright caters to various needs for website owners seeking efficient customer support solutions.', NULL, '["Customer Support","Chat Solutions","Automation"]');
